==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: magnetic tape
<hw>magnetic tape</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A long thin plastic ribbon
coated with iron oxide or other ferromagnetic material, used to record
audio or video signals digital data in the form of small magnetized
regions on the tape; it is a common <isa>digital data storage
medium</isa> for computer information.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> mag tape, tape.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>magnetic variation</ent>⟦br⟧
